    DefaultUserTaskListener.afterQuestionnaireResponseCreate(ProcessPluginApi api, Variables variables, CreateQuestionnaireResponseValues createQuestionnaireResponseValues, org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.QuestionnaireResponse afterCreate)
    Override this method to execute code after the QuestionnaireResponse resource has been created on the DSF FHIR server

    Default implementation will add an output parameter to the start Task with a reference to the created QuestionnaireResponse resource if DefaultUserTaskListener.taskOutputSystem, DefaultUserTaskListener.taskOutputCode and DefaultUserTaskListener.taskOutputVersion are set with not blank values.

    Use field inject in BPMN to set value.
